{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "de4c6e5b-6a1b-44d4-b4ea-0f4f5df8f001",
        "name": "Dllni - Restaurant Owner Module",
        "description": "## Base URL and Prefix\n- Collection variable `{{baseUrl}}` defaults to `http://Dllni.test`.\n- Prefix: `/api/v1`.\n- Owner app routes are mostly under `/api/v1/restaurant-owner/*`.\n\n## Authentication\n- All endpoints in this collection require Sanctum token.\n- Header: `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`.\n\n## Props Format (Request / Response Contract)\n- Path props: `{id}` in docs and `{{id}}` in Postman variables.\n- Query props: mostly camelCase (`perPage`, `page`, `range`, `from`, `to`).\n- Validation errors (422): `{ \"message\": string, \"errors\": { \"field\": [string] } }`.\n\n## Common Enums\n- performance range: `today | week | month | year | custom`\n- product availability mode: `available | sold_out_today | manual_unavailable`\n- offer status: `active | scheduled | expired | all`\n\n## Notes\n- Restaurant context is inferred from authenticated owner account; do not send restaurant id for owner-scoped endpoints.\n- Order item edits are allowed only while order status is `pending` or `accepted`.",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://Dllni.test"
        },
        {
            "key": "token",
            "value": ""
        },
        {
            "key": "orderId",
            "value": "1"
        },
        {
            "key": "itemId",
            "value": "1"
        },
        {
            "key": "productId",
            "value": "1"
        },
        {
            "key": "employeeUserId",
            "value": "1"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Restaurant Profile",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Get current restaurant",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/restaurant-owner/restaurant",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "restaurant-owner",
                                "restaurant"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Returns the owner restaurant context for the authenticated user.\n\nProps:\n- Headers: Authorization bearer token.\n\nResponse (200):\n- data.id, data.name, data.slug\n- data.primaryImage, data.images[]\n- data.city, data.district, data.phone"
                    },
                    "response": [
                        {
                            "name": "200 OK - restaurant",
                            "status": "OK",
                            "code": 200,
                            "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
                            "header": [],
                            "cookie": [],
                            "body": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Sham Kitchen\",\n    \"slug\": \"sham-kitchen\",\n    \"description\": \"Levantine cuisine\",\n    \"city\": \"Aleppo\",\n    \"district\": \"New Aleppo\",\n    \"phone\": \"+963944000333\",\n    \"primaryImage\": \"https://example.test/storage/media/r1/main.jpg\",\n    \"images\": []\n  }\n}"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
